{"tid":1678154,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聼]要聲援維吾爾人，而唔係新疆或東突","createTime":"2019-10-27T13:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T09:00:34.000Z","uid":274161,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d43bfb805589c81b376c59805f03cc341aa3f5b4","tid":1678154,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:39:45.000Z","msg":"最近大家都話要聲援新疆，亦都有人話係東突<br />\n<br />\n但小弟覺得，應該更加有針對性，係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聲援維吾爾人</strong></span></span>。何解？<br />\n<br />\n1. 新疆都有漢人，而維吾爾人係主要的鎮壓對象；聲援新疆的説法不明確<br />\n2. 東突通常被分離主義者用來代指新疆；除此之外，東突也是「土耳其斯坦伊斯蘭黨」（East Turkestan Islamic Movement）的簡稱，已被聯合國安理會、美國和英國列入恐怖主義組織名單（wiki）。所以，請慎用「東突」。"},{"pid":"dc0d7c4faa67048cedc835f630692f9644464148","tid":1678154,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"巴絲請將今日的警暴情況/記者中槍的tweets推上國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4fzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=7810cc7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n入<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> /task1 </span></span>  retweet and like all links<br />\n入<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> /task2</span></span>    retweet and like all links"},{"pid":"a733cbfdee51c4e18ee95ecdb43979e3762c0b25","tid":1678154,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55bc798b6721f2a2d8e048db0a667bf6e266f0de","tid":1678154,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d43bfb805589c81b376c59805f03cc341aa3f5b4","tid":1678154,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:39:45.000Z","msg":"最近大家都話要聲援新疆